Class Vector

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.math.linearalgebra.Vector

    public class Vector
extends Object
implements NumberVector<Vector,Double>
    Provides a vector object that encapsulates an m x 1 - matrix object.
